{"tid":778034,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂嘅大學文化真係不知所謂","createTime":"2018-08-13T11:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T16:09:35.000Z","uid":86695,"like":53,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3d359bdbfb3d7c023104cb48504155ef36226f5d","tid":778034,"uid":86695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人覺得曾幾何時大學已經無文化可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文化：人類所創造嘅精神財富，好似文學、藝術、教育、科學、禮貌、節日等等<br />\n但現在的大學生玩ocamp玩到無節制，時不時都有淫亂的事發生。dem beat講粗口已經變成疊馬英雄主義的象徵。<br />\n最大問題係啲大學生覺得玩淫game講粗口係無問題。完全無羞恥心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全港入到大學的人只有不多於20%，應該係貢獻社會，做一個有品德的人<br />\n或者好多人會覺得我呢番說話係好老套，我係更加不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好希望作為年輕人的我地，應該係做一個受人尊敬，而唔係俾人話係廢青，讀屎片的學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大學之道：在明明德，在親民，在止于至善。知止而后有定，定而后能靜，<br />\n靜而后能安，安而后能慮，慮而后能得。物有本末，事有終始，知所先后，<br />\n則近道矣"},{"pid":"d2d298727b021448479918a850fc733fcabc192b","tid":778034,"uid":142872,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"有實力就可以入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人想知你鍾唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164087ec994e380b7195dbf570bd70659656c62a","tid":778034,"uid":86695,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"利申:HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係扮清高，只係當年輕人埋怨社會點點點嘅時候，諗諗自己立身處世嘅態度先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd048912127b4e7cd9c34ba7ac65ddf6ba920bf","tid":778034,"uid":200252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"agger 已經形式大於意義"},{"pid":"1a6af54829ef0c9dfb5d7d3276a618022b4407c7","tid":778034,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:41:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa33c0c6cfa9edaff15e156cc2adc78d03740d35","tid":778034,"uid":86695,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:47:28.000Z","msg":"或者好多大學生覺得我地dem返個beat先！好威，可以從中得到自信。但好多都無諗過真正的意義係乜。其實不如問下自己點解要入大學，將來想做乜，先係對自己的前途有幫助。如果你係大學都隨波逐流，無自己的一套想法。將來出到真正的社會大學，就更加失去方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3fadf744d663adef8a623568c84ba3c4061efb","tid":778034,"uid":196077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"扑多野結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主走轉後門真係看透世事！"},{"pid":"4d42c3ffb6191400b667f47bc898d65aa537fdff","tid":778034,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"認同樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da6810ab787cb9ed3c908bb91d2150a2a63317c","tid":778034,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"7f09bcf0ac255aa38e1d4879d1e9b5ca699bc207","tid":778034,"uid":198822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"認同 但係引文可唔可以唔好用殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd4db6c7f2fa07aaebfd19fbe8563e38249ae34","tid":778034,"uid":3823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"其實dem beat都dem左幾十年啦 傳統話改就改咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我覺得依家個問題係d人唔記得左dem beat嘅意義 為dem而dem <br />\n<br />\n利申：搞camp但唔鐘意dem beat,好憎粗口beat"},{"pid":"63133170f9b8142b5f0195babf919ac18eeda94a","tid":778034,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T12:00:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬是咪走後門狗融入唔到正統大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkg